                  <summary>Anaphora of Our Lady Mary ascribed to Cyriacus of Bǝhǝnsa, ቅዳሴ" ማርያም", God of the Luminaries, Prayer of the Covenant, ጸሎተ፡ ኪዳን፡, “For the Sake of Peaceful Holy Things,” በእንተ፡ ቅድሳት፡ ሰላማዊት፡, Mystagogia, , ትምህርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡, Anaphora of Our Lord, ቅዳሴ፡ እግዚእ፡, Lamentations of the Virgin, ሰቆቃወ፡ ድንግል፡</summary>
